Initialize an API Client

library(dplyr)

library(metagenomicsClientR)
basePath = 'https://cmgd-telemetry-whnnxetv4q-uc.a.run.app'
client = ApiClient$new(basePath = basePath)
api = DefaultApi$new(apiClient = client)
